  "key_strengths": [
    "Forced concrete decision output (start/narrow/redesign/stop) converts assessment into action",
    "True novelty vs pseudo-novelty separation prevents wasted effort on cosmetically novel but substantively weak topics",
    "Explicit resource feasibility audit before novelty assessment prevents over-optimistic recommendations",
    "Prohibition on fabricating publication precedents and dataset availability prevents false feasibility signals"
